2025-09-23T22:09:05Z,16401519_us,Tributary to Williston Reservoir,AI,"Large stream with complex habitat and diverse cover including deep pools, boulders, large and small woody debris, and undercut banks. A canyon section approximately 100m long was located 100m upstream of the Modeste FSR bridge, containing multiple cascade steps up to 1m high with deep downstream pools. At the upper end of the site, the channel deflected against steep gully walls.
